2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>引體上升真係懶人專用<br />\n我做四組，每組五下已經有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔止圓肩，仲有頸椎退化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頸椎退化可以做咩運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3845bc8429a79c91eb9a73ca8037027eca93d7a1","tid":285112,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>引體上升真係懶人專用<br />\n我做四組，每組五下已經有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔止圓肩，仲有頸椎退化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頸椎退化可以做咩運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜運動都做得嘅，但就盡量唔好郁條頸<br />\n有時打羽毛波大力殺，chok到條頸，都會要痛到暫停一兩分鐘嘅"},{"pid":"493c673e61260fa1b30234f828684102c0d5a389","tid":285112,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>引體上升真係懶人專用<br />\n我做四組，每組五下已經有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔止圓肩，仲有頸椎退化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n引體好累,點算懶</blockquote><br />\n就係快攰先快有效果<br />\n其他拉到眼瞓都未攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34562f1367b3a546ed3dc71b0b272b4de763d93","tid":285112,"uid":98551,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做掌上壓啦<br />\n<br />\n你個胸肌會大 擴大 , 會推後兩邊膀頭, 就唔會縮埋膊頭</blockquote><br />\n唔好玩啦<br />\n練胸唔練背會搞到圓肩<br />\n應該練背"},{"pid":"822eadd3bb98b6a1521251649d72d0e205b9a21f","tid":285112,"uid":104784,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做掌上壓啦<br />\n<br />\n你個胸肌會大 擴大 , 會推後兩邊膀頭, 就唔會縮埋膊頭</blockquote><br />\n唔知你假膠定真心....咪撚鳩up啦<br />\n乜撚野胸肌大會推後膊頭，你up乜鳩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識就咪撚亂鳩咁up啦，過度強壯既胸肌只會幾肩胛骨拉向前，如果背肌相對下弱就只會令寒背同圓肩更嚴重...<br />\n樓主本身都有寒背圓肩既問題，首要一定係要練好背肌將肩胛骨拉返後<br />\n仲有....正確既push up做法係要你推左上去後幾背同肩做返個拱起既狀態，對於一個已有圓肩既人黎講絕對係令佢更加習慣唔好既posture&hellip;....<br />\n而做背部肌肉既訓練大多要求做延胸幾肩胛骨拉後後既posture,除左本身練到肌肉幾posture改善外，更加係俾樓主一個多次練習同養成正確posture既習慣<br />\n<br />\n總結：要改善圓肩一定唔係做push up,係要練背，你唔好鳩up教壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce0865dec8b44c6aae129fbf5d473b3678b3715","tid":285112,"uid":104784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做掌上壓啦<br />\n<br />\n你個胸肌會大 擴大 , 會推後兩邊膀頭, 就唔會縮埋膊頭</blockquote><br />\n唔知你假膠定真心....咪撚鳩up啦<br />\n乜撚野胸肌大會推後膊頭，你up乜鳩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識就咪撚亂鳩咁up啦，過度強壯既胸肌只會將肩胛骨拉向前，如果背肌相對下弱就只會令寒背同圓肩更嚴重...<br />\n樓主本身都有寒背圓肩既問題，首要一定係要練好背肌將肩胛骨拉返後<br />\n仲有....正確既push up做法係要你推左上去後將上背同肩做返個拱起既狀態咁樣<br />\n對於一個已經有圓肩既人黎講絕對係令佢更加習慣唔好既posture&hellip;....<br />\n而做背部肌肉既訓練大多要求做廷胸同將肩胛骨拉後<br />\n除左本身練到肌肉幾posture改善外<br />\n更加係俾樓主一個多次練習同養成正確posture既習慣<br />\n<br />\n總結：要改善圓肩一定唔係做push up,係要練背，你唔好鳩up教壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"31a6fc15e190c3c2e3bdaf8a3dd5bbad4c5ff05b","tid":285112,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"游水"},{"pid":"e6bb170d1a24afd9e92b5c06e9cc0100cc5ad930","tid":285112,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"寒背首先要放鬆番肩部肌肉，專登坐直反而感覺越攰係因為肩部左右力量不平衡，越想坐直就越撚攰，肩部左右力量不平衡嘅特徵係肩膊肌肉硬過石頭"},{"pid":"d8a89bab054856d8467da53278a13ee564f3f860","tid":285112,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"仲有寒背同圓肩成因係唔同的"},{"pid":"0c49f7d86ef538736c645fa955a42eab1744354e","tid":285112,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有寒背同圓肩成因係唔同的</blockquote><br />\n點知自己係咩"},{"pid":"31e6a773172ac810d1f36fa78ec13aa56733d9c3","tid":285112,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有寒背同圓肩成因係唔同的</blockquote><br />\n點知自己係咩</blockquote><br />\n圓肩個膊頭會彎向前，寒背會出現類似A字膊情況"},{"pid":"a33ba788861025cef571bb16b72fe7d3817dd3e5","tid":285112,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"我係圓肩+頸前傾"},{"pid":"515b1df969ad584741095ec5382688f3ae47789d","tid":285112,"uid":113934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係圓肩+頸前傾</blockquote><br />\n我都係 可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1110f84883a0f99e26008388d56da3aa21517dd5","tid":285112,"uid":58080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係圓肩+頸前傾</blockquote><br />\n我都係 可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3ce2bd25d9d3b254e2614a0ebb207747d16bc0","tid":285112,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寒背首先要放鬆番肩部肌肉，專登坐直反而感覺越攰係因為肩部左右力量不平衡，越想坐直就越撚攰，肩部左右力量不平衡嘅特徵係肩膊肌肉硬過石頭</blockquote><br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db9a7912f91241a53c485fc13906398f3bf396","tid":285112,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b090aceb9e7af8196afc169613a5349e4804e9b"